<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">

		<h1>About Me</h1>

		<hr>

		<div class="row">

			<div class="col-md-4">

				<%= image_tag "montenegro.jpg", width: 250, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-image' %>

				<div class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
							<div class="progress">
								<div 
									class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
									role="progressbar"
									aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
									aria-valuemax="100"
									style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
								>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>With nearly five years of development experience, I'm empathic to customer's views. It's easy to ignore
						challenging puzzles, but I thrive on those puzzles and drive a project to completion. With clear communication and
						flexibility I help manage expectations throughout the entire process.</p>

				<p>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controler="jobHistory"
					>
						Job History
					</button>
					<button
						class="btn btn-primary"
						type="button"
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#educHistory"
						aria-expanded="false"
						aria-controler="educHistory"
					>
						Education
					</button>
				</p>

				<p>
					<div id="history">
						<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
							<div class="card card-block">
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-med-4">
										<%= image_tag "ccds.png", alt: "CustomCall Data Systems", class: 'job-history-image' %>
									</div>
									<div class="col-med-8">
										<p><strong>Senior Programmer Analyst</strong> - Maintained and enhanced proprietary telecommunications, customer, inventory, and billing management SaaS J2EE application using waterfall and agile methodologies to ensure successful deployment</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="card card-block">
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-med-4">
										<%= image_tag "uscellular.png", alt: "US Cellular", class: 'job-history-image' %>
									</div>
									<div class="col-med-8">
										<p><strong>Application Developer II</strong> - Customized software for provisioning personal mobile devices. Developed custom code on mediation platform for rating and billing customers (Inter-mediatE) by utilizing standard SDLC practices and unit testing</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="collapse" id="educHistory">
							<div class="card card-block">
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-med-4">
										<%= image_tag "msoe.png", alt: "Milwaukee School of Engineering", class: 'job-history-image' %>
									</div>
									<div class="col-med-8">
										<p>Graduated with a Bachelor's of Science in Management with an emphasis in Information Systems</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="card card-block">
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-med-4">
										<%= image_tag "nwtc.png", alt: "Northeast Wisconsin Technical College", class: 'job-history-image' %>
									</div>
									<div class="col-med-8">
										<p>Graduated with a Microcomputer Specialist Associate's degree</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

	</div>
</div>
